name: Moll's Map of Lancashire (c.1724)
description: Hermann Moll's county map of Lancashire. Moll was one of the most prolific cartographers of the early 18th century.
notes:
Hermann Moll (c.1654-1732), German-born London cartographer.
Published numerous county maps and atlases.
Lancashire map from 'A Set of Fifty New and Correct Maps' (c.1724).
Also produced maps for 'The Compleat Geographer' and various atlases.
NLS Lancashire county maps page may have this digitized.
